caption.text: MSI to quantify pairwise interactions. The table presents pairwise MSI for examples from the literature. The higher the value of MSI, the better is the benefit the organism derives through this interaction. The references in Column 1 and 2 pertain to the source of the respective GSMMs. The value in bold in each row indicates the MSI of the organism that benefits from the interaction.
